@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title Rolul unui router

[LAN A] as lana
[Router] as r
[LAN B] as lanb

lana --> r : pachete IP
r --> lanb : pachete IP

note right of r
  Router:
  - conecteaza retele
  - decide next hop / interfata
  - foloseste tabela de rutare
  - poate filtra / modifica (NAT, ACL)
end note
@enduml
